timing_enable...ckgating_check(25.10)    timing_enable...ckgating_check(25.10)

Name
       timing_enable_clock2clock_clockgating_check

Syntax
       timing_enable_clock2clock_clockgating_check

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Enables clock-to-clock clock gating checks.

       When set to true, the software performs clock to clock gating checks at
       gating  elements.  For clock to clock gating checks, the frequency of a
       clock arriving at the reference side of a check should be equal  to  or
       greater  than the frequency of the clock arriving at the signal side of
       the check.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

